<br>
    If you would open your eyes you could see that the only reason he is second in points is because when hes on the track no one else gets a chance to finish a race.  Multiple times this year I have seen him take out many good karts.  For example this past Friday night.  The #29 kart and #4 kart were having a good clean battle and in came #21 which booted one of them and caused both of them to crash hard.  Thats a shame because the #4 kart was the fastest on the track and the only one on my stop watch that had anything for the leader IF he had a chance to get to him and that was cut short due to stupidity.  The track needs to pick up the black flag and use it.   I was just in the stands watching and seen all this so I know the track workers had to see it.  I just think its a shame that week after week they let him come in there and do this.  Something needs to be done before he hurts someone. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bkartanddriver.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kartndriver>kartndriver</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>ezOP</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FF9300>(8/11/03 3:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkartanddriverfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=47.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: medium class</span><hr size=1> One of the post on this page was just a little out of bounds and was removed by me. We're sorry for the posting and hope it doen't affect the rest of the page. Kevin Ward #911 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F9FBFD><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> KY FLASH</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#FF9300>(8/12/03 12:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkartanddriverfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=47.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td>